*Chinese: (''Simplified Chinese'') [[渐弱]] / (''Traditional Chinese'') [[漸弱]] (''pinyin:'' jianruo)
*German: [[Diminuendo]]
*Korean: [[점점 약해지는 음]] (jeomjeom yakhaejineun eum)

